# Google Sheets API credentials
# Get these from Google Cloud Console → Service Account → Keys

GOOGLE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_EMAIL=your-service-account@your-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
GOOGLE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
GOOGLE_SHEET_ID=your-google-sheet-id-from-url

# How to set up:
# 1. Create a Google Cloud project
# 2. Enable Google Sheets API
# 3. Create a Service Account and download JSON key
# 4. Share your Google Sheet with the service account email (Editor access)
# 5. Copy the Sheet ID from the URL: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/{SHEET_ID}/edit
# 6. Add these variables in Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables
